.TH Num.exp 3 2025-04-30 "Tomo man-pages"
.SH NAME
Num.exp \- base-e exponentiation
.SH LIBRARY
Tomo Standard Library
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.BI Num.exp\ :\ func(x:\ Num\ ->\ Num)
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the exponential function $e^x$ for a number.


.SH ARGUMENTS

.TS
allbox;
lb lb lbx lb
l l l l.
Name	Type	Description	Default
x	Num	The exponent. 	-
.TE
.SH RETURN
The value of $e^x$.

.SH EXAMPLES
.EX
>> (1.0).exp()
= 2.7183
.EE
